who saved his life

98
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,000
to a Noble Woman.

99
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,120
What's your opinion?

100
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,310
I think

101
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:29,310
the attempted assassination
on His Majesty

102
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,190
