116
00:07:57,510 --> 00:07:58,350
Right.

117
00:07:58,510 --> 00:07:59,480
Your Grace,

118
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,870
I have prepared

119
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,480
for tomorrow.

120
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,400
Good.

121
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:08,560
I haven't seen

122
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,310
Prince of Ning An for ages.

123
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:11,910
Yes.

